issue.title: A survey immediately switches to the next page when changing the number input value
issue.body:
Run the following Angular sample: https://codesandbox.io/s/surveyjs-angular-forked-nxwjs7.

Use arrow buttons to change a number value. A survey immediately switches to the next page (`goNextPageAutomatic: true`).

Expected behavior: a survey doesn't switch to the next page when changing the numeric value with arrows. An input should wait until a user clicks outside the input and submits the value (like in [this React sample](https://plnkr.co/edit/PlveQsB1ycX8cSwE)).

issue.title: A survey immediately switches to the next page when changing the number input value
issue.body:
Run the following Angular sample: https://codesandbox.io/s/surveyjs-angular-forked-nxwjs7.

Use arrow buttons to change a number value. A survey immediately switches to the next page (`goNextPageAutomatic: true`).

Expected behavior: a survey doesn't switch to the next page when changing the numeric value with arrows. An input should wait until a user clicks outside the input and submits the value (like in [this React sample](https://plnkr.co/edit/PlveQsB1ycX8cSwE)).
